Gaussian path integrals, and show good agreement\nwhen compared with intense Monte Carlo simulations for the target examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Sep 2021 17:25:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 08:12:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Sep 2021 14:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 13:17:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-14"}
