idations. A sampling test\nbased on human tele-operation is processed on the oral cavity model with\nexcellent success rate. The proposed TOOS robot demonstrates a highly promising\nsolution for tele-operated, safe, cost-effective, and quick deployable COVID-19\nOP swab sampling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Sep 2021 10:02:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-21"}
